name: pyrel_base

task:
query
         call | range(0 100 1 v)
          get | data_people_csv_id(v id)
          get | data_people_csv_name(v name)
          get | data_people_csv_age(v age)
         call | query
                  get | RawData([0, 1, 2, 3, 4, ... 98, 99] ["P-00007333", "P-00007530", "P-00007649", "P-00007666", "P-00007809", ... "P-00016637", "P-00016681"] v2 id2)
                 bind | data_people_csv_id(v2 id2)

         call | query
                  get | RawData([0, 1, 2, 3, 4, ... 98, 99] ["Tommy Roman", "Alan Hatfield", "Clayton Wilson", "Susan Jones", "Eric Horn", ... "Rodney Ortiz", "Ian Romero"] v3 name2)
                 bind | data_people_csv_name(v3 name2)

         call | query
                  get | RawData([0, 1, 2, 3, 4, ... 98, 99] [18, 16, 15, 25, 48, ... 50, 37] v4 age2)
                 bind | data_people_csv_age(v4 age2)

         call | query
                  get | RawData([1, 2, 3, 4, 5, ... 98, 99] ["ACCT-00010539", "ACCT-00010668", "ACCT-00010800", "ACCT-00010864", "ACCT-00010901", ... "ACCT-00018734", "ACCT-00018750"] v5 account)
                 bind | data_people_csv_account(v5 account)

         call | query
                  get | RawData([1, 15, 19, 24, 35, 40, 44, 50, 55, 73, 78, 86, 88, 89, 90] [true, true, true, true, true, true, true, true, true, true, true, true, true, true, true] v6 criminal)
                 bind | data_people_csv_criminal(v6 criminal)

         call | make_identity(["Person", name, age, id] person)
         bind | person | Person name(name) age(age) csv_id(id)
         call | query
                  get | data_people_csv_account(v account2)
                 bind | person | Customer account(account2)

         call | query
                  get | data_people_csv_criminal(v criminal2)
                 bind | person | Criminal

task:
query
         call | range(0 200 1 v)
          get | data_transactions_csv_id(v id)
          get | data_transactions_csv_date(v date)
          get | data_transactions_csv_from(v from)
          get | data_transactions_csv_to(v to)
          get | data_transactions_csv_amount(v amount)
          get | customer | Customer csv_id(from)
          get | customer2 | Customer csv_id(to)
         call | query
                  get | RawData([0, 1, 2, 3, 4, ... 198, 199] ["TXN-00004052", "TXN-00004148", "TXN-00004291", "TXN-00004482", "TXN-00004598", ... "TXN-00024404", "TXN-00024443"] v2 id2)
                 bind | data_transactions_csv_id(v2 id2)

         call | query
                  get | RawData([0, 1, 2, 3, 4, ... 198, 199] ["2023-10-12", "2023-05-11", "2023-05-22", "2023-10-03", "2023-03-17", ... "2023-02-21", "2023-04-01"] v3 date2)
                 bind | data_transactions_csv_date(v3 date2)

         call | query
                  get | RawData([0, 1, 2, 3, 4, ... 198, 199] ["P-00013130", "P-00009338", "P-00015723", "P-00012137", "P-00015268", ... "P-00010228", "P-00012262"] v4 from2)
                 bind | data_transactions_csv_from(v4 from2)

         call | query
                  get | RawData([0, 1, 2, 3, 4, ... 198, 199] ["P-00015417", "P-00010602", "P-00010882", "P-00016527", "P-00010882", ... "P-00015556", "P-00015578"] v5 to2)
                 bind | data_transactions_csv_to(v5 to2)

         call | query
                  get | RawData([0, 1, 2, 3, 4, ... 198, 199] [5214, 2969, 1246, 1023, 1096, ... 29689, 17877] v6 amount2)
                 bind | data_transactions_csv_amount(v6 amount2)

         call | make_identity(["Transaction", id, date, customer, customer2, amount] transaction)
         bind | transaction | Transaction txn_id(id) date(date) from_(customer) to_(customer2) amount(amount)
name: rule1

task:
query
          get | transaction | Transaction from_(from_) to_(to_) amount(amount)
          get | from_ | name(name)
          get | to_ | name(name2)
       return | transaction name name2 amount

query
          get | customer | Customer
          get | criminal | Criminal
          get | transaction | Transaction from_(customer) to_(criminal)
         bind | transaction | Suspicious
         call | query
                  get | transaction | amount(amount)
                 bind | transaction | ImmediateReview review_reason("Large transaction to criminal")
                 call | >(amount 40000)
